LINE 1: SELECT rank() OVER (PARTITION BY four, ORDER BY ten) FROM te...
                                               ^
SELECT count() OVER () FROM tenk1;
ERROR:  count(*) must be used to call a parameterless aggregate function
LINE 1: SELECT count() OVER () FROM tenk1;
               ^
